WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:23.030
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:24.280
BOBBY: Daddy!

00:00:28.844 --> 00:00:31.279
DAD: Are you going up?

00:00:31.279 --> 00:00:33.383
MOM: I went last time.

00:00:33.383 --> 00:00:36.041
BOBBY: Daddy!

00:00:36.041 --> 00:00:38.050
DAD: All right.

00:00:41.026 --> 00:00:43.010
BOBBY: Daddy!

00:00:43.010 --> 00:00:44.810
DAD: I'm coming, Bobby.

00:00:44.810 --> 00:00:45.700
I'm coming.

00:00:45.700 --> 00:00:46.950
BOBBY: Hurry!

00:00:49.480 --> 00:00:49.970
Dad.

00:00:49.970 --> 00:00:51.500
DAD: What seems to be
the problem, sport?

00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:53.468
BOBBY: It was a monster.

00:00:53.468 --> 00:00:55.928
A big green monster
with lots of arms.

00:00:55.928 --> 00:01:00.356
It was the same one
I saw before.

00:01:00.356 --> 00:01:03.480
DAD: Bobby, we've talked
about this before.

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:05.730
There's no such thing
as monsters.

00:01:05.730 --> 00:01:08.095
BOBBY: No daddy, it's true.

00:01:08.095 --> 00:01:11.406
There is a monster,
and he's this big.

00:01:11.406 --> 00:01:12.825
DAD: Now Bobby--

00:01:12.825 --> 00:01:17.500
BOBBY: It's true dad, and it
says it's going to get me.

00:01:17.500 --> 00:01:19.905
DAD: That's not going
to happen.

00:01:19.905 --> 00:01:22.580
Your mom and I are just
downstairs, and we're not

00:01:22.580 --> 00:01:24.470
going to let anything
happen to you.

00:01:24.470 --> 00:01:25.280
BOBBY: But--

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:26.580
DAD: No buts.

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:27.670
You're a big boy now.

00:01:27.670 --> 00:01:30.620
You need to stop being
afraid of the dark.

00:01:30.620 --> 00:01:33.010
Monsters don't appear just
because the light goes out.

00:01:36.146 --> 00:01:37.390
Goodnight son.

00:01:37.390 --> 00:01:39.040
I'll see you in the morning.

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:42.586
Remember, you're
perfectly safe.

