00:02:53.464 --> 00:02:57.610
BOBBY: Uh, whoa.

00:02:57.610 --> 00:02:59.218
Whoa!

00:02:59.218 --> 00:03:00.715
Whoa!

00:03:00.715 --> 00:03:02.711
Whoa!

