00:04:18.559 --> 00:04:21.781
MOM: What was that?

00:04:21.781 --> 00:04:23.710
DAD: It's coming from
Bobby's room.

00:04:27.950 --> 00:04:29.630
Bobby?

00:04:29.630 --> 00:04:31.200
Son?

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:32.080
Son?

00:04:32.080 --> 00:04:34.075
Are you OK?

00:04:34.075 --> 00:04:38.240
BOBBY: Yes daddy, just
like you said.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:39.600
I'm perfectly safe.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:48.940
